22
00:02:53,697 --> 00:02:55,115
I'm leaving sooner than expected.

23
00:02:55,657 --> 00:02:57,742
<i>Where are you right now? I'll be there.</i>

24
00:02:59,119 --> 00:03:00,287
No.

25
