<i>many times before, but we still need
to say our last goodbyes.</i>

33
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:24,477
<i>We do need to say it again.</i>

34
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:26,521
<i>So tell me where you are right now.</i>

35
00:03:26,605 --> 00:03:27,606
Don't hang up!

36
00:03:28,898 --> 00:03:29,858
Listen to me.

37
00:03:30,358 --> 00:03:32,986
Tell me what you see. I can find you.

38
00:03:43,204 --> 00:03:44,372
Jeong Hyeok.

39
00:03:46,333 --> 00:03:47,417
I love you.

40
00:03:56,593 --> 00:03:57,636
Let's go!

41
00:04:13,485 --> 00:04:16,446
<i>The person you have reached
is not available.</i>

42
