GU SEUNG-JUN

43
00:04:34,089 --> 00:04:38,426
<i>The phone is either turned off or out
of the service area and cannot be reached.</i>

44
00:05:00,448 --> 00:05:03,284
<i>Jeong Hyeok? You need to come home now.</i>

45
00:05:04,327 --> 00:05:06,162
-My gosh.
-What's going on?

46
00:05:06,246 --> 00:05:07,414
