52
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:27,767
He's fuming mad, but that only makes him
even more attractive.

53
00:05:27,851 --> 00:05:29,811
-Exactly.
-Right?

54
00:05:51,583 --> 00:05:53,084
You're here, Ri Jeong Hyeok.

55
00:05:54,419 --> 00:05:56,421
