is bound to change all the time.

67
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:17,293
You little shit.

68
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:20,213
You're finished.

69
00:07:25,311 --> 00:07:26,299
Take him.

70
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:33,560
