-My goodness.

72
00:07:36,104 --> 00:07:37,146
-Oh, no.
-Make way!

73
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:39,190
-Why are they taking him?
-Jeong Hyeok!

74
00:07:39,357 --> 00:07:41,901
-My gosh.
-What do we do?

75
00:07:41,985 --> 00:07:43,736
Jeong Hyeok! What should we do?

76
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:46,030
-Gosh!
-My goodness.

77
00:07:46,531 --> 00:07:47,991
Gosh, what the heck is happening?

78
00:07:48,074 --> 00:07:49,659
Shouldn't we tell them?

79
00:07:50,201 --> 00:07:53,162
