for the first and the last time.

739
00:57:51,419 --> 00:57:52,629
Are you saying

740
00:57:54,297 --> 00:57:56,049
you are the person

741
00:57:57,216 --> 00:57:59,177
who was playing the song that day?

742
00:58:03,723 --> 00:58:04,891
How is this...

743
00:58:08,645 --> 00:58:09,937
I can't believe this.

744
00:58:11,481 --> 00:58:12,482
That day,

745
00:58:14,317 --> 00:58:16,235
I was really lonely.

746
00:58:18,154 --> 00:58:19,113
I truly

747
00:58:21,366 --> 00:58:23,993
wished to die then.

748
00:58:25,244 --> 00:58:28,164
I wanted to go to a beautiful place

749
00:58:29,040 --> 00:58:31,125
and quietly disappear

750
00:58:31,709 --> 00:58:33,586
so I didn't trouble anybody.

751
00:58:34,879 --> 00:58:36,631
