757
00:59:03,995 --> 00:59:05,051
Listen to me carefully.

758
00:59:07,265 --> 00:59:08,215
Tomorrow,

759
00:59:09,122 --> 00:59:10,790
you will go back home.

760
00:59:45,158 --> 00:59:46,576
There was a suspicious car

761
00:59:46,659 --> 00:59:49,412
using a temporary license plate

762
00:59:49,495 --> 00:59:52,790
in the military village at that time,
so we tracked the car.

763
00:59:53,082 --> 00:59:55,752
And the car went toward Seojaegol
and then disappeared.

764
00:59:55,835 --> 00:59:58,337
That's where Director
of the General Political Bureau lives.

765
01:00:00,256 --> 01:00:03,301
So let's say that woman went there
by that car.

766
01:00:03,760 --> 01:00:05,781
Even so, we don't know
if she's still there.

767
01:00:06,220 --> 01:00:07,680
They might have killed her already.

768
01:00:07,764 --> 01:00:11,058
The security officer working in Seojaegol

769
01:00:11,225 --> 01:00:13,978
happens to be my college friend,
so I did some research.

770
01:00:14,562 --> 01:00:18,316
I heard there were cars coming in,
but no cars have gone out yet.

771
01:00:22,787 --> 01:00:23,779
Sir.

772
01:00:24,739 --> 01:00:28,242
If you go there now,
you can catch something huge.

773
01:00:39,170 --> 01:00:40,546
Present arms.

774
01:00:42,882 --> 01:00:45,259
The car behind this is with me.
Let it pass too.

775
01:00:45,343 --> 01:00:46,886
Yes, sir!

776
01:01:04,921 --> 01:01:06,697
Hello, sir.

777
01:01:07,532 --> 01:01:09,659
