to discuss with you,

778
01:01:09,742 --> 01:01:11,619
and I'm in front of your house now.

779
01:01:12,203 --> 01:01:14,121
Do you have a moment?

780
01:01:16,374 --> 01:01:19,001
I'm sorry I came so suddenly, sir.

781
01:01:19,085 --> 01:01:21,045
